content: Xander's now not just predicting; he's influencing market trends with his ethical trading. It's surreal seeing him guide the financial world towards fairness. The demo with the next institution is going to be epic.

Just got off the phone with the next financial institution. They're excited to see Xander in action. We're fine-tuning his ethical trading model for the big show. It's a high-stakes game, but we're ready.
